            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Locus <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>adsig</abbr><ex>natus</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berio</ex></expan> Iulio Iuliano <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Ma<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Iulio <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>atoribus</ex></expan> aedium sacr<supplied reason="lost">arum et operum</supplied> <lb n="4"/>publicorum <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>dedic</abbr><ex>at--</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Insteio Celere <supplied reason="lost">et <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung der Dedikation der Inschrift in das Jahr 128, in welchem Ti. Iulius Iulianus curator und zugleich Q. Insteius Celer consul suffectus waren.</p>
            </div>
